WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.280 --> 00:00:06.200
Is this connected?

2
00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:09.160
Right.  So you're  up to speed
 with what we're up against.

3
00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:14.400
The DCI has been locked up and our entire
 case against APT hangs in the balance.

4
00:00:14.960 --> 00:00:17.120
Now, we all know this is complete rubbish.

5
00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:18.240
The boss might be new to

6
00:00:18.240 --> 00:00:21.560
cyber crime, but we know she wouldn't
 do anything to jeopardise the case.

7
00:00:22.080 --> 00:00:24.320
Besides, we didn't make anything up.

8
00:00:24.720 --> 00:00:26.760
We got APT fair and square.

9
00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:29.920
The only chance we've got to prove
 that the boss hasn't done

10
00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:32.680
anything wrong is to prove
 the whole thing is a setup.

11
00:00:33.720 --> 00:00:36.000
Now I can stall the CPS for a bit.

12
00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.320
So we got 30 minutes
 to prove she's innocent

13
00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:41.800
or the whole case will come tumbling down.

14
00:00:41.800 --> 00:00:45.600
She called me from custody and gave us
 permission to get into her files,

15
00:00:46.080 --> 00:00:48.160
but didn't want to give me
 the password over the phone

16
00:00:49.160 --> 00:00:50.760
Whilst I'm stalling the lawyers

17
00:00:50.800 --> 00:00:52.680
I'll co-ordinate tasks from
my office here.

18
00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:55.400
And if something comes up,
 I'll give you a call.

19
00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:59.200
And if I find anything to help,
 I'll send it to your police email.

20
00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:03.120
The first job is to
 get into the DCI's system.

21
00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:06.000
Although she didn't
 tell me her password over the phone,

22
00:01:06.320 --> 00:01:10.240
she said she's been meaning to change it
after reading an article last week.

23
00:01:10.480 --> 00:01:14.480
I've attached the article, which is a list
of commonly used passwords.

24
00:01:14.880 --> 00:01:17.160
On the off chance,  she hasn't got
around  to changing it yet.

25
00:01:17.480 --> 00:01:19.640
Might want to run through the list.

26
00:01:19.640 --> 00:01:21.960
Good luck, detectives. We're all counting on ya.

